<h2>AI Documentation</h2>

<p>Every substantive AI partner conversation that informed your Report must be documented in the <a href="/foundations/ai-documentation-protocol/">AI Documentation Template</a> and submitted alongside the Report. Same rules as the Unit 0 Source Dossier: log the prompt, the response, your OPVL on the response, and the "one thing the AI got wrong" entry. If you used the <a href="/ai-partners/planet-hunter/">Planet Hunter</a> to evaluate your exoplanet, the <a href="/ai-partners/systems-diagrammer/">Systems Diagrammer</a> to refine a feedback loop, or the <a href="/ai-partners/the-source-evaluator/">Source Evaluator</a> to OPVL a NASA archive entry — document each one. Missing documentation triggers the K/U gate above.</p>

